    <p id="p_cml_bgk_54b"
      product="author developer editor authorEclipse developerEclipse editorEclipse"><ph
        keyref="product"/> includes several <xref keyref="glossentry_perspective"
          ><term>perspectives</term></xref> and <xref
        href="oxygen-editing-modes.dita#oxygen-editing-modes">editing modes</xref> to help you
      accomplish a wide range of tasks. Each <term>perspective</term> and editing mode also includes
      a large variety of helper views, menu actions, toolbars, and contextual menu functions.</p>
    <p product="json"><ph keyref="product"/> includes several editing modes
        (<uicontrol>Text</uicontrol>, <uicontrol>Grid</uicontrol>, <uicontrol>Author</uicontrol>,
      and <uicontrol>Design</uicontrol>) and a large variety of helper views, menu actions,
      toolbars, and contextual menu functions.</p>
    <p product="author developer editor json" id="p_dml_bgk_54b">There are various ways that you can
        <xref href="dockable-views-and-editors.dita#dockable-views-and-editors">configure the layout
        of the views or editors</xref>, and you can <xref
        href="configure-toolbars.dita#configure-toolbars">customize the toolbars</xref>.</p>
